Specify the default domain to be used for generating ObjectNames_when no source-level metadata has been specified._

The default is to use the domain specified in the bean name_(if the bean name follows the JMX ObjectName syntax)_ else,_the package name of the managed bean class._@see MetadataNamingStrategy#setDefaultDomain
